namedLocations.description: A ZIP Code is a postal code used by the United States Postal Service (USPS) in a system it introduced in 1963. The term ZIP is an acronym for Zone Improvement Plan; it was chosen to suggest that the mail travels more efficiently and quickly (zipping along) when senders use the code in the postal address. The basic format consists of five digits. An extended ZIP+4 code was introduced in 1983 which includes the five digits of the ZIP Code, followed by a hyphen and four additional digits that reference a more specific location.
namedLocations.name: ZIP Code

namedLocations.description: Gujarat (/ˌɡʊdʒəˈrɑːt/, Gujarati: [ˈɡudʒəɾɑt] ) is a state on the western coast of India with a coastline of 1,600 km (990 mi) – most of which lies on the Kathiawar peninsula – and a population in excess of 60 million. It is the sixth largest Indian state by area and the ninth largest state by population. Gujarat is bordered by Rajasthan to the northeast, Daman and Diu to the south, Dadra and Nagar Haveli and Maharashtra to the southeast, Madhya Pradesh to the east, and the Arabian Sea and the Pakistani province of Sindh to the west. Its capital city is Gandhinagar, while its largest city is Ahmedabad. The Gujarati-speaking people of India are indigenous to the state. The economy of Gujarat is the fifth-largest state economy in India with ₹14.96 lakh crore (US$220 billion) in gross domestic product and a per capita GDP of ₹157,000 (US$2,300). Gujarat ranks fifteenth among Indian states in human development index.

transcript.text: Hello, welcome to on picture.
In this video we will learn about how to set up hire a designer.
Let's talk about key features and benefits.
If customers do not have their design nor they want to browse design from existing templates or create a new design, then they can hire a designer.
With this option.
Hire a designer helps your customer to get a customized design as per their choice from a ready gated designer.
You can set designer cost in the product specific settings.
Let's have a look into the admin.
So first of all, we need to go to product, select the product and click on action and edit.
Here you can see in configuration we have product type buttons where you have to check hire a designer and save it.
Now when you go to the storefront here in the price calculator you will see there is a option to select hire a designer, yes or no.
So if you select yes, then you will see there is a button higher design for us or you can rename it from the back end.
So you have to go to the setting here you can change the label for your designer button and also you can put the pricing for the designer cost.
So as you can see over here, the price will get added into the total price.
And when we click on higher designer button, it will go to the additional option page where we can see the designer information including the additional form fields.
So these additional form fields we can add from the back end.

So we need to go to the store configuration manage form field section and here you can add a new field form and select the form field type higher designer and also you can choose for a specific product.
So from the list you can select the product in which you want to show the higher designer field.
So in this way you can use higher designer option.
Thank you for watching this video.
In case of any further query, feel free to connect with us.
